  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\r\n\r\n2.18.1\r\n\r\n### What happened?\r\n\r\nTest fails with `RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded` after upgrading to Hardhat `2.18.1` from `2.12.1-ir.0`.\r\n\r\nI could reproduce the error on Ubuntu 22 with Node 20 and on MacOS Ventura with Node 18.\r\n\r\n### Minimal reproduction steps\r\n\r\n1. Check out https://github.com/ProjectOpenSea/seaport/ @ `6d8bf57d`\r\n2. `yarn`\r\n3. `yarn upgrade hardhat@2.18.1`\r\n4. `npx hardhat test --grep \"Reverts on changed chainId\"`\r\n\r\n### Search terms\r\n\r\n_No response_",
